<P><ADD>The Possibility of Gods Forsaking a people, That have been visibly near &amp; dear to him...Set forth in a Sermon, Preached at Weathersfield; Nov. 21. 1678.</ADD></P>
<P><ADD>By Mr. Joseph Rowlandson.</ADD></P>
<P><ADD>Cambridge: Printed by Samuel Green. 1682.</ADD></P>
